{
  "stem": "25639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But our little group has disintegrated when the key organizer came to the United States with her-- [LAUGHS] with her family, and to the state of New York.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, after that, we broke up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I mentioned, I also sang in a-- in a choir group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, it wasn't sophisticated, but it was great fun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I enjoyed going to the library and look at books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The library was not very large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, it was just the opposite-- very small.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I almost finished all the books that they had there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They really didn't have very many books, and I especially used to complain that there are no pictures in them, which I looked forward-- I looked forward to whenever I could put my fingers on some of these.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I liked-- I liked stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I liked [NON-ENGLISH], for example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a whole series about this man called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was funny, and I would laugh.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For example, he would go to Budapest from a small town, and I envisioned myself going to Budapest from our little small town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he, he's-- he-- in the book, his impressions about this-- this big city were, were they put people on top of the, [LAUGHS] on top of the roofs, and they look down upon him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, he was talking about the statues.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and he was always afraid that they were going to fall on him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was so funny, just reading about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not as a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As an adult, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at age 14, when I was taken out of high school to-- because we were shipped to Auschwitz, at that point I had nine, ten-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] seven.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
